ApproxsimClient.proj
Class ProjectionErrorHandler

java.lang.Object
  ApproxsimClient.proj.ProjectionErrorHandler

public class ProjectionErrorHandler
extends Object

This class is used to handle the errors obtained in the coordinate conversion process.
